import React from "react";

export const UploadIcon = () => (
  <svg
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    fill="none"
    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
    strokeWidth={2}
    stroke="currentColor"
    className="w-6 h-6"
  >
    <path
      strokeLinecap="round"
      strokeLinejoin="round"
      d="M12 16V4m0 0l4 4m-4-4L8 8m-4 8h16"
    />
  </svg>
);
